{
  "stem": "16503.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 371.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they came and they were very like brutal, in a mannerism, brutal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and went through the apartment and, you know, threw everything about, and then stomped out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they did not take my father with them or anything like that, which that was on many occasion, I think on most occasions they did take the man of the-- of the house with them.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then later on, either they'd return with a broken mouth or something, or didn't return at all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, that did not happen to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The other time, which is actually a very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] humorous [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] story, the janitor called that somebody in a SS uniform, meaning an SS uniform, was asking for my father and is coming upstairs.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, the doorbell rang and there is this huge German standing there with the SS band and the uniform and the click.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He was, you know, just as you imagine them and this they were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he says, oh, Anthony, how nice to see you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he threw his arms around him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I thought, oh, my dear god.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was one of his-- my father's former client from the Sudetenland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came into the living room and they chatted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I must tell you that it was a very, very uncomfortable feeling having this SS sitting there, all dolled out in his SS uniform, and he wanted to know if he could help Father with anything or any kind.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I just was like, my god, what is he doing?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was kind of a humorous story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never heard of this man and I don't want to hear from this man.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
